properties.areaDesc: Point Isabelle to Lower Entrance of Portage Canal MI
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 9 at 4:11AM EST until January 9 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Marquette MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...South winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and
waves 6 to 9 feet occurring.

* WHERE...Point Isabelle to Lower Entrance of Portage Canal MI.

* WHEN...Until 7 PM EST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 PM EST THIS EVENING
